For this you will need the following 

- A bot made in https://discord.com/developers/applications

To learn how to make a discord bot in the developer portal visit https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ibtXXoMxaho

Next you will need bot designer for discord 

you can find the web app for pc here:
https://botdesignerdiscord.com/app/

For android find it here:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jakubtomana.discordbotdesinger&hl=en_US&gl=US

and for ios users you can find it here 
https://apps.apple.com/us/app/bot-designer-for-discord/id1495536477

After that your all set

(You need an Mobile Phone/Tablet to host the bot)

Now we can move onto the next step in the adding bot file
